title: New Creator: Steve Olsher (Club Pod / Podcast Magazine
body:
Name: Steve Olsher 

Socials:
https://podcastmagazine.com/
https://www.instagram.com/ThePodcastMag/
https://clubpod.club/ 24K members 

Info:
Steve Olsher is the Founder and Editor & Chief of Podcast Magazine. Steve also runs multiple clubs including Club Pod on Clubhouse. With over 100,000 followers across multiple social media platforms, Steve and Podcast Magazine are leading the way in the world of podcasts!  

Use Cases:
Pod Coin will drive their Podcast Magazine website allowing users to gain inside access to the latest podcasts, guests, and an exclusive newsletter. 
On Clubhouse, Pod coin will allow members and coin holders to ask questions to guests, tip guests, and support the club. 

Community Treasury Grant Tier: $1,000

A 'yes' will approve Steve Olsher and Podcast Magazine with a $1,000 Community Treasury Gift Coin grant.

A 'no' will deny this proposal.
